## Limitations

The primary limitation of this report is the reliance on secondary sources and interpretations of Sherry Turkle's work. While the sources provide a comprehensive overview, direct access to the full text of "Alone Together" would offer a more nuanced understanding of her arguments. Additionally, the report is based on data available up to October 2023, and newer developments in technology and societal trends may not be reflected.

